AltText: A murky pool of decaying organic matter near Fionn Loch, Assynt.
Title: Tangle
CaptionAbstract:
No doubt the most scenic view in the whole of the Assynt-Coigach National Scenic Area.

If you need everything to be epic sunrises and the Aurora Borealis, then life might often fall short of your expectations. If you can find contentment in a murky pool of decaying organic matter, then no matter what happens, you're probably going to be OK.
